About Hilliard Lyons Trust Company, LLC

Hilliard Lyons Trust Company, LLC is one of the largest independent trust companies in Kentucky. 
We provide asset management, trust administration and estate planning services for a wide array of high net-worth clients and institutions.  
Hilliard Lyons Trust Company also serves as trustee and as agent for trustee of numerous types of trusts, including revocable living trusts, charitable remainder trusts, life insurance trusts, total return trusts, marital trusts, and credit shelter trusts. 
We have a highly talented group of professionals with a strong commitment to delivering excellent service and solid long-term investment results.  Our professionals have a total of over 200 combined years of experience directly serving Personal Trust clients.  When you initiate a relationship with Hilliard Lyons Trust Company, you can feel confident that you and your family will receive a high level of attention and consideration from our professional staff.







