Jack spent 20 years with Frost Brown Todd where he was a Partner, specializing in Estate and Tax Planning. Prior to that, he spent 20 years with First Security National Bank & Trust Company as an Executive Vice President in the trust department. Jack has B.A. and J.D. degrees from the University of Kentucky. He has served as Board Chair for Hospice of the Bluegrass and Board Chair for Salvation Army of the Bluegrass. He also served on the Board of Directors and the Investment Committee for the Bluegrass Community Foundation. Jack joined Hilliard Lyons in 2016.
